{"ProductId":"240","Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Louver","ShortDescription":"Versatile and unique, plantation style Louver doors","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/orlandotnahlouvershowcase.webp?sfvrsn=e83ed7a2_1","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-louver","Overview":"<h3>Built for Coastal Charm and Lasting Strength</h3><h4>Robust 5-Layer Construction</h4><p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Louver features a steel core, high-performance insulation, and a second steel layer, all wrapped in a moisture-resistant composite cladding and overlay for extra durability and a gorgeous finish.</p><h4>Authentic Wood Appeal</h4><p>The faux wood composite is molded from real wood pieces, capturing the texture and grain of Clear Cypress or Mahogany&mdash;so you get the warmth of wood without the maintenance.</p><h4>Customizable Design</h4><p>Choose from twelve unique louvered door designs, optional windows, and decorative hardware. Available in eight standard finishes or personalize even further with over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> custom colors.</p><h4>Superior Insulation</h4><p>Each door packs 2\" of <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane foam insulation</a>, delivering R-values from 18.4 to 20.4 for year-round comfort and energy savings.</p><h4>Weather-Resistant Options</h4><p>For homes in high-wind zones, <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> is available for extra peace of mind.</p><h4><strong>Environmental Assurance</strong></h4><p>Clopay\r\n doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay\r\n    doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Where Craftsmanship Meets Innovation</h3><p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Louver garage door is built with five thoughtfully engineered layers that combine the best of beauty and brawn. At its core, you&rsquo;ll find a heavy-duty steel base for strength and structure. This is surrounded by thick, 2-inch Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation, which not only boosts the door&rsquo;s energy efficiency, but also helps keep your garage quieter and more comfortable year-round. Another steel layer adds extra durability, while the exterior is finished with a composite cladding and overlay that mimic the look and feel of real wood without the worries of warping, rotting, or cracking.</p><p>Maintenance is simple: the composite materials are moisture-resistant and built to handle everything from coastal humidity to harsh winters. The multi-layer steel skin is protected by Clopay&rsquo;s advanced rust-prevention system, including hot-dipped galvanizing, a protective metal oxide coating, and a tough, baked-on finish. Every door comes with a replaceable vinyl bottom weather seal in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer to keep the elements out, and a patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg; to help prevent injuries during maintenance. This is a door designed for everyday ease, lasting curb appeal, and dependable performance.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-canyon-ridge-louver320.webp?sfvrsn=e30813be_4\" alt=\"\" sf-size=\"28612\" /><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Composite Overlay</li><li>Composite Cladding</li><li>Steel</li><li>2\" Intellicore&reg; Polyurethane Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Canyon Ridge Louver","DisplayIndex":5,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/canyon-ridge-louver","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Louver garage door comes in a variety of finishes designed to enhance its natural woodgrain texture and complement your home&rsquo;s exterior. Choose from classic wood-inspired stains like Medium, Dark, Walnut, and Slate for a warm, inviting look. For a more modern edge, there are also Black, White, Bronze, and Charcoal finishes, which are available on select models and exclusively in the Mahogany composite.</p><p>If you want something truly unique, the door&rsquo;s two-tone option lets you mix colors between the steel base layer and the composite overlay, giving you even more control over your door&rsquo;s style. Plus, the Color Blast&reg; program offers over 1,500 custom paint colors, so you can find the perfect shade to match your vision.</p><p><em>*Available on select models.<br />Black, white, bronze and charcoal only available in Mahogany.<br />Steel surfaces have a woodgrain texture.<br />Two-tone option available. One color for the base layer (steel) and one color for the top layer (composite overlay).</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>Available only on Design 52, the Canyon Ridge&reg; Louver garage door offers several top section window designs so you can personalize your door&rsquo;s look and let in just the right amount of natural light. The lineup includes rectangular and square window configurations like REC11, REC13, REC14, SQ23, and SQ24. You can get a wide, open feel with larger windows or a more classic, balanced look with smaller panes, whatever suits your style.</p><p>These top section options help you control the look&mdash;from clean-lined and modern to traditional and welcoming&mdash;while also allowing you to brighten your garage&rsquo;s interior. No matter which window layout you choose, each one is designed to complement the louvered panels and enhance your home&rsquo;s curb appeal.</p>","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Louver offers a range of hardware choices to add both style and function to your garage door. Every door comes standard with durable spade lift handles, which provide a classic look and easy grip. If you want to elevate your door&rsquo;s aesthetic, upgrade to optional handle styles like spear, colonial, decorative lift handles, or even a ring door knocker for added charm.</p><p>To complement these handles, you can also choose from a variety of escutcheon plates and twisted &ldquo;L&rdquo; handles, adding subtle but distinctive details that enhance your door&rsquo;s overall appeal.</p><p>For hinges, there&rsquo;s a selection of styles including spade, spear, and colonial strap hinges, all designed to match your chosen hardware and reinforce the door&rsquo;s structure. These decorative and functional hardware pieces let you tailor your Canyon Ridge&reg; Louver door to fit your home&rsquo;s architectural style perfectly.</p>","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (4-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr4l-d21-rec13-afp143r.webp?sfvrsn=8ae1d536_3","Id":"29","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-4-layer","DisplayIndex":4,"ShortDescription":"Stylish, low maintenance and insulated faux wood garage doors","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (4-Layer)"},{"Title":"Gallery<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/gallery-steel-ug-long-rec14-595.webp?sfvrsn=a7ceae04_9","Id":"12","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/gallerysteel","DisplayIndex":8,"ShortDescription":"Grooved panel steel carriage house garage doors","AlternativeText":"Gallery Steel"},{"Title":"Coachman<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup>","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-imag